parameters: *Thank you for your hard work seeing to all the tales*
That voice echoes inside my head.
(Where…am I…there's no more stories to distort?)
*You have distorted all of the girls' tales*
(I see…but, what do you get from all of this?)
let me go back to the Real World)
*…your body no longer exists in the Real World*
(What!? You've got to be kidding me…!)
(Nobody…? What is the meaning of this…)
*You've been sucked into these distorted tales*
(I can't stay in this crazy world anymore!...let me go!!)
*But this is the world you desired, right? Hehe…ahahaha!*
"Manipulating people and creatures to your liking like that,
…did you get off watching me get humiliated?
(Watching you get raped was incredibly exciting!!)
"…then this world is perfect for you♪
You were chosen for this book.
"This book reflects the distortion of a twisted mind.
And steals the heart…and devours its very existence!
"It does nothing to a pure heart but…
You lived up to the book's expectations.
(Eat…!? I was eaten by a book…!?)
(Damn it! No kidding…this place…you've got to be joking!!)
"That's right. It's nice to finally meet you.
(I'm sorry…about what I did to you!)
your body no longer exists so…
No matter how frightened we were,
"Didn't they teach you when you were a child?
Bad things always come back to bite you…hehehe♪
(I just did as I was told by the book…!)
The book said 'it'll change form to suit the reader's mind',
"You just wanted to see us all messed up, right?
You enjoyed hearing us moan ahhn♥ ahhn♥, right?
Yes, of course…because you're a boy!
"But…you can't do that to a girl who doesn't want to, okay?
Don't you know that it's wrong?
(Damn it…! Damn it!!! Making a fool out of me!!)
(I can do whatever I want to your fates!!)
(What is going to happen to me…please tell me Schnee…)
You will be just like use…
You'll become a resident (cast) of this book's world.
"And…you'll be responsible for entertaining new readers.
(I'm going to be a cast of fairy tales…!?)
(No…! Live forever in this crazy world…!?)
You were thinking about lewd things
so the world became like that, you hear?
"If the reader is a wonderful person,
(I don't want to act out someone else's mind…!)
"You manipulated us to your heart's content, too, right?
Anyway, there's nowhere to go back to
so it's more fun to just accept it♪
"You've taken home after home from me.
You're…now a part of our family.
we can live happily ever after here forever♪
maybe it's not so bad to stay here…)
To the world of fairy tales we live in…
into the comfort of the darkness and voices.
◆(株)ビタースウィートエンタテインメント
武藤FP/ふらいんぐパンジャンドラム
